## 10. Code Conventions

### API Response Format
```typescript
// Backend returns this envelope -- ALWAYS unwrap in frontend
interface ApiResponse<T> {
  data: T;
  meta?: { total: number; page: number; limit: number };
  message?: string;
}
```

### Auth Guards
```typescript
// {{BACKEND_FRAMEWORK}} guard pattern
@UseGuards({{AUTH_GUARD_NAME}})
@{{TENANT_DECORATOR}}()  // Multi-tenant isolation
```

### Multi-Tenant Queries
```typescript
// EVERY database query MUST include tenant isolation
where: {
  {{TENANT_ID_FIELD}}: {{TENANT_ID_SOURCE}},
  deletedAt: null,  // Soft delete filter
  ...otherFilters,
}
```

### Import Conventions
```typescript
// Path alias
import { Component } from '{{PATH_ALIAS}}/components/...';
import { apiClient } from '{{PATH_ALIAS}}/lib/api';
```

